Source: univention-pkgdb
Section: univention
Priority: optional
Maintainer: Univention GmbH <packages@univention.de>
Build-Depends: debhelper, python-dev, python-support, univention-config-dev, ucslint
Standards-Version: 3.8.2

Package: univention-pkgdb
Architecture: all
Pre-Depends: univention-postgresql (>= 2.0.1-5)
Depends: univention-config-registry, postgresql-client, univention-pkgdb-tools 
Description: UCS - PkgDB
 This package contains server-side-components for the Univention package database.
 .
 It is part of Univention Corporate Server (UCS), an
 integrated, directory driven solution for managing
 corporate environments. For more information about UCS,
 refer to: http://www.univention.de/

Package: python-univention-pkgdb
Architecture: all
Depends:  ${python:Depends}, python-apt, python-pygresql, python-dns, univention-config-registry
Provides: ${python:Provides}
Conflicts: univention-pkgdb-lib (<<1.0.4)
Description: UCS - PkgDB
 This package contains python libraries needed for all Univention package database components.
 .
 It is part of Univention Corporate Server (UCS), an
 integrated, directory driven solution for managing
 corporate environments. For more information about UCS,
 refer to: http://www.univention.de/

Package: univention-pkgdb-tools
Architecture: all
Depends: univention-config-registry, python-univention-pkgdb
Recommends: postgresql-client
Description: UCS - PkgDB-Tools
 This package contains client-side-tools for the Univention package database.
 .
 It is part of Univention Corporate Server (UCS), an
 integrated, directory driven solution for managing
 corporate environments. For more information about UCS,
 refer to: http://www.univention.de/

Package: univention-pkgdb-lib
Architecture: all
Depends: python-univention-pkgdb
Description: Transition package
 Package to ease upgrading from old package
 python-univention-pkgdb to the new package.  This package
 can be purged at anytime once the
 python-univention-pkgdb package has been installed.
